29:46.137 --> 29:47.620
I'm just sayin' like no,
I wouldn't.

29:47.655 --> 29:50.448
Well, then, sir,
would you like to learn,

29:50.448 --> 29:55.068
because I am in fact
a certified safety instructor

29:55.103 --> 29:58.172
