our Second Amendment rights,

30:06.172 --> 30:09.586
in true red-blooded
American fashion I might add.

30:09.586 --> 30:10.793
Yeah, absolutely.

30:10.793 --> 30:13.241
You guys are gonna celebrate
by shooting a machine gun?

30:13.275 --> 30:14.586
Yeah.

30:14.586 --> 30:16.517
I own several of 'em.

30:16.586 --> 30:21.103
It's our God-given right.

30:21.137 --> 30:23.965
