I can't do it you know.

30:24.000 --> 30:25.620
Well, there you go.

30:25.655 --> 30:28.344
That's an even better reason
to learn.

30:28.413 --> 30:31.620
Gun safety is important
if you have children.

30:31.655 --> 30:34.413
Picture the scenario,
your kid finds a gun.

30:34.448 --> 30:37.103
Thinks it's a toy.

30:37.103 --> 30:38.172
Can you imagine
the consequences

30:38.241 --> 30:41.275
of somethin' like that
happenin'?

30:41.310 --> 30:44.448
Downright unthinkable.

30:44.448 --> 30:46.172
Here, check this out.

30:46.206 --> 30:49.448
- Whoa, oh, no, no, I can't.
- It's alright, safety's on.

30:49.482 --> 30:50.620
Just don't put your finger
on the trigger,

30:50.655 --> 30:52.931
- it's uh, right there.
- Okay.

30:52.931 --> 30:55.275
