ain't gonna bite you.

30:55.275 --> 30:56.310
Alright.

30:58.241 --> 30:59.275
Whoa, Jesus Christ!

30:59.344 --> 31:00.000
Oh, s-- I'm sorry, I'm sorry,
I didn't mean to.

31:00.068 --> 31:02.689
- Dude, I'm sorry.
- Listen.

31:02.724 --> 31:06.068
You never ever point a gun
at somethin'

31:06.137 --> 31:07.689
