31:07.724 --> 31:11.482
You understand what I'm sayin',
Mr. Bell?

31:11.517 --> 31:12.551
GREYSON:
I'm sorry.

31:12.620 --> 31:13.965
Well, I'm just sayin'
if you remember anything,

31:14.000 --> 31:15.482
remember that.

31:15.482 --> 31:17.379
Gun's not a toy.

31:17.413 --> 31:19.379
It should be treated
with respect.

31:19.448 --> 31:20.379
I got it.

31:20.448 --> 31:21.655
Jesus.

31:21.689 --> 31:25.413
Well, I believe you, but here.

31:25.482 --> 31:26.896
- The safety's right here--
- No.

31:26.965 --> 31:29.034
And you just make sure
that sucker's on first.

31:29.068 --> 31:30.241
No, I shouldn't.

31:30.310 --> 31:31.344
That's alright.

31:31.344 --> 31:33.379
Here, take it.

31:35.034 --> 31:37.000
No, we don't--
you just hold it right there.

31:37.000 --> 31:38.000
Yeah.

31:38.034 --> 31:39.413
Alright.

31:39.482 --> 31:42.172
Now, listen,
when you pull the trigger,

31:42.172 --> 31:44.310
this thing is gonna kick back
at you.

31:44.344 --> 31:46.551
That's gonna cause the barrel
to climb,

31:46.586 --> 31:48.482
so you have to kinda just--

31:48.482 --> 31:51.000
Here, there you go.

31:52.344 --> 31:54.517
Just like that.

31:54.551 --> 31:56.241
Feels good, doesn't it?

31:56.310 --> 32:00.034
Ugh, no, I-- here.

32:00.068 --> 32:01.517
I'm never gonna shoot
anything like that.

32:01.551 --> 32:02.758
Yeah, I understand.

32:02.793 --> 32:05.586
A gun that size
can be intimidating.

32:05.586 --> 32:06.620
Kinda like the young
college girl

32:06.655 --> 32:08.137
