she gets somethin'

32:10.551 --> 32:11.551
she can handle.

32:13.241 --> 32:14.724
If you catch my drift.

32:14.758 --> 32:15.724
Yeah.

32:18.413 --> 32:19.551
WINSLOW:
I won't hold it against you.

32:20.344 --> 32:22.068
LIAM:
Hey, you want a beer?

32:22.068 --> 32:24.068
