32:59.068 --> 33:00.137
GREYSON:
Yeah, sure.

33:00.206 --> 33:02.103
Everybody did.

33:02.137 --> 33:04.655
I do believe you are correct,
sir.

33:04.689 --> 33:07.655
I reckon about every boy did.

33:07.655 --> 33:10.103
Well, this ain't that
much different than those,

33:10.137 --> 33:11.655
