35:31.620 --> 35:33.241
Shit, Liam, I was just joking.

35:33.275 --> 35:36.586
I know that, but he doesn't.

35:36.620 --> 35:39.896
- Just give him a break.
- You're right, of course.

35:39.931 --> 35:42.758
